      abortion: { o: 2, short: 'Health grounds ≤24 wks', statement: 'Lawful up to 24 weeks on physical/mental-health grounds with two doctors’ approval (Abortion Act 1967, as amended), and later for serious risk or foetal anomaly; a 2026 reform decriminalised women for ending their own pregnancy in England & Wales.', ev: 'law', cert: 'established', asOf: '2026', src: 'crr' },
